---
import '../styles/global.css';

const pageTitle = "Conoce a Keiner";
const identity = {
  name: "Keiner Mendoza",
  country: "Venezuela",
  occupation: "Desarrollador Web",
  hobbies: ["Diseñar", "Aprender Nuevas Tecnologías", "Piano"],
};

const skills = ["HTML", "CSS", "Tailwindcss" ,"Python", "JavaScript", "Django", "React", "Astro", "Writing Docs"];

const skillColor = "brown";
const textCase = 'uppercase';
const fontWeight = 700;
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>

		<style define:vars={{skillColor, fontWeight, textCase}}>
			h1 {
			  color: purple;
			  font-size: 4rem;
			}
			.skill {
				color: var(--skillColor);
				font-weight: var(--fontWeight);
				text-transform: var(--textCase);
			}
		  </style>

	</head>
	<body>
		<nav>
			<a href="/">Home</a>
			<a href="/about/">About</a>
			<a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
		</nav>
		
		<section>
		<h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
		<p>Soy un desarrollador web con experiencia en la creación de apps usando diferentes lenguajes de programación</p>
		<p>Me gusta mantenerme aprendiendo cosas brindo soluciones de desarrollo</p>
		<p>Originalmente me enfoocaba en el backend, principalmente usando python y django. Actualmente tambien desarrollo frontend con JavaScript y <b>Astro</b> </p>

		<p>Here are a few facts about me:</p>

		<ul>
			<li>My name is {identity.name}.</li>
			<li>Soy de  {identity.country} and I work as a {identity.occupation}.</li>
			
			{identity.hobbies.length >= 2 &&
				<li>Two of my hobbies are: {identity.hobbies[0]} and {identity.hobbies[1]}</li>
			}
		</ul>
		
		<p>Habilidades</p>
		<ul>
		{skills.map((skill) => <li class="skill">{skill}</li>)}
		</ul>
		</section>
	</body>
</html>
